---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';

const pageTitle = "Terms of Service - smartly.sale";
const pageDescription = "Read our terms of service and understand the rules for using smartly.sale.";
---

<MainLayout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-accent/50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8 border border-border">
        <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-2">
          <strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2025
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground">
          By accessing or using smartly.sale, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. 
          If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Use of Our Website</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
            smartly.sale provides product reviews, recommendations, and affiliate links to Shopee Philippines. 
            You agree to use our website only for lawful purposes and in accordance with these terms.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            You must not use our website in any way that causes damage to the website or impairs 
            its availability or accessibility.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
            smartly.sale is a participant in affiliate marketing programs, including Shopee's affiliate program. 
            This means we may earn commissions when you make purchases through our links.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
            The prices you pay are not affected by our affiliate partnerships. We only recommend products 
            we believe will provide value to our community.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            We are not responsible for the products, services, or actions of third-party merchants 
            linked from our website.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Product Information</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
            We strive to provide accurate product information, but we cannot guarantee that all 
            descriptions, prices, and availability are 100% accurate or current.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Product prices, specifications, and availability are subject to change without notice. 
            Always verify details on the merchant's website before making a purchase.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
            All content on smartly.sale, including text, images, logos, and graphics, is the property of 
            smartly.sale or its content suppliers and is protected by copyright laws. You may not reproduce, 
            distribute, or create derivative works without our express written permission.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Product images may be provided by merchants or manufacturers and are used for 
            informational purposes only.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">User Comments and Content</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
            If you submit comments, reviews, or other content to our website, you grant us a 
            non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, and publish that content.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            You agree not to post content that is offensive, defamatory, or infringes on the 
            rights of others. We reserve the right to remove any content at our discretion.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-3">
            smartly.sale and its affiliates shall not be liable for any damages arising from your use of 
            our website or reliance on information provided. This includes direct, indirect, 
            incidental, or consequential damages.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            We make no warranties about the accuracy, reliability, or completeness of the information 
            on our website. Use of our website is at your own risk.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">External Links</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            Our website contains links to third-party websites (including merchant sites). 
            We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of these external sites. 
            Links are provided for convenience only and do not imply endorsement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be 
            effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use of the website after changes 
            constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Governing Law</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            These Terms of Service are governed by the laws of the Republic of the Philippines. 
            Any disputes shall be resolved in Philippine courts.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
        <div class="bg-background rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-border">
          <p class="text-muted-foreground">
            If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please visit our 
            <a href="/contact" class="text-[#FF6600] hover:underline font-semibold">Contact Page</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
